Dominous

1. How to install

1.1 Linux (tested under Ubuntu 9.10):

user@machine:~$ sudo aptitude install python-pygame
user@machine:~$ sudo apt-get install python-setuptools
user@machine:~$ sudo easy_install PyOpenGL PyOpenGL-accelerate

1.2 Windows:

No instructions yet


2. Creating new computer players

player.py - python file inheriting from main player class
image.png - 500x500 image of the player. If no image is provided i'll use a default one
Directory name will be used as player name

